{"tid":2302343,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【周梓樂死因研訊】救護隊目車上檢查　梓樂右瞳孔較大、無法度血壓　或腦受創內出血","createTime":"2020-11-27T05:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T09:47:55.000Z","uid":77536,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fd2d53cb3c995acdc35a205dbef8b037d3de583a","tid":2302343,"uid":77536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T05:00:55.000Z","msg":"【立場新聞】科大生周梓樂死因研訊今日（27日）踏入第 10 天，接送梓樂到醫院，並在救護車上為梓樂檢查的救護隊目出庭作供。他透露，在救護車上，梓樂的右眼瞳孔較左眼瞳孔大，有機會腦受創；梓樂睜眼反應、說話反應及肌肉動作反應全數最低分，處於昏迷狀態。而且，救護員無法為梓樂取得血壓度數，有機會血壓過低未能取得，懷疑是內出血。（全文）<br />\n<br />\n#20201127新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E5%91%A8%E6%A2%93%E6%A8%82%E6%AD%BB%E5%9B%A0%E7%A0%94%E8%A8%8A-%E6%95%91%E8%AD%B7%E9%9A%8A%E7%9B%AE%E8%BB%8A%E4%B8%8A%E6%AA%A2%E6%9F%A5-%E6%A2%93%E6%A8%82%E5%8F%B3%E7%9E%B3%E5%AD%94%E8%BC%83%E5%A4%A7-%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%A6%E8%A1%80%E5%A3%93-%E6%88%96%E8%85%A6%E5%8F%97%E5%89%B5%E5%85%A7%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25A2%2593%25E6%25A8%2582%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%25A0%2594%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E6%2595%2591%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E9%259A%258A%25E7%259B%25AE%25E8%25BB%258A%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%259F%25A5-%25E6%25A2%2593%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%258F%25B3%25E7%259E%25B3%25E5%25AD%2594%25E8%25BC%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E8%25A1%2580%25E5%25A3%2593-%25E6%2588%2596%25E8%2585%25A6%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%2589%25B5%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A1%2580%2F&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpPsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=bd4e5958\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25A2%2593%25E6%25A8%2582%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%25A0%2594%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E6%2595%2591%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E9%259A%258A%25E7%259B%25AE%25E8%25BB%258A%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%259F%25A5-%25E6%25A2%2593%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%258F%25B3%25E7%259E%25